What the Post Is About
The post provides a clear, well-written explanation of the Cauchy Momentum Equation, one of the fundamental equations in continuum mechanics.
It uses the simple analogy of squeezing a stress ball to explain how forces balance inside any material (solid or fluid). The core message is:
Net force on any small piece of material only occurs when stress changes across space.
